title: Mwsaglangw anglai mwsaglangw
lyrics:
Mwsaglangw anglai mwsaglangw
Jisuni jwnwmao mwsaglangw
(A)
Bwi David nwgwrni goki bwithelhemao
Mwdwu golini naodra sahao
 
Bwi hatorkia lama dinthidwng
Sanja desh ni gwnwkhw fwrkhou
 
Iswra esegrap onbai songsarkhou
Saselo bisakhou jwngnw hwbai
 
Dukhu gwila jwngha daha gweila
Phwrbuanw jwngkhou onkhang kabai
 
Jisu rajani sari janai jwng
Jwngbw jiao dinwi sari mwnbai
